{"type":"item.completed","item":{"id":"item_14","type":"agent_message","text":"The existing logical definition for `UBERON:0000961` already says it is a paravertebral ganglion part of the thoracic sympathetic trunk, so the requested label change is consistent with the current axioms. For `UBERON:0002835`, the logical genus is dorsal root ganglion, so I can remove the explicit `is_a` to the paravertebral term without leaving it unclassified."}}
