{"type":"item.completed","item":{"id":"item_69","type":"command_execution","command":"/bin/bash -lc \"sed -n '1,220p' PR_COMMENTS.md\"","aggregated_output":"## Summary\n\nThis addresses issue #3475 by clarifying the thoracic sympathetic ganglion term and removing the incorrect dorsal root ganglion classification.\n\nChanges made:\n- Renamed `UBERON:0000961` from \"thoracic ganglion\" to \"thoracic paravertebral ganglion\".\n- Replaced the ambiguous old label with a `RELATED` synonym.\n- Removed broad/ambiguous automatic exact synonyms for \"ganglion of thorax\" and \"thorax ganglion\".\n- Simplified the `UBERON:0000961` definition so it mirrors the existing logical definition: paravertebral ganglion part of the thoracic sympathetic nerve trunk.\n- Removed `is_a: UBERON:0000961` from `UBERON:0002835` \"thoracic dorsal root ganglion\"; it remains logically defined as a dorsal root ganglion extending fibers into the root of thoracic nerve.\n- Added `term_tracker_item` links to issue #3475 on both affected terms.\n\n## Rationale\n\nThe issue text points out that dorsal root ganglia are not paravertebral/sympathetic ganglia. The existing ontology confirmed that `UBERON:0000961` was logically defined as a paravertebral ganglion in the thoracic sympathetic trunk, while `UBERON:0002835` was a dorsal root ganglion incorrectly asserted as an `is_a` child of that term. Renaming `UBERON:0000961` makes the intended scope explicit and removing the asserted parent prevents thoracic dorsal root ganglion from being classified under a sympathetic/paravertebral ganglion.\n\n## Validation\n\nCompleted checklist:\n- Read `__issue_context__.json`.\n- Checked affected stanzas with `obo-grep.pl`.\n- Checked proposed parent consistency for dorsal root ganglion, paravertebral ganglion, and thoracic sympathetic nerve trunk.\n- Checked `src/patterns/dosdp-patterns`; no ganglion-specific DOSDP pattern was present.\n- Used `obo-checkout.pl` and `obo-checkin.pl` for the term edits.\n- Reserialized `src/ontology/uberon-edit.obo` with `robot convert`.\n- Ran non-mutating syntax validation with `robot convert -i src/ontology/uberon-edit.obo -f obo -o /tmp/uberon-edit-issue-3475-validation.obo`.\n- Ran `git diff --check`.\n\nCommitted locally as `6fc559d`.\n\n@dragon-ai-agent\n\n","exit_code":0,"status":"completed"}}
